+---------------------------------------------------------------------+
                              MINI QUESTS
+---------------------------------------------------------------------+

  Mini quests are fun, typically fairly simple quests that players of
  various levels can accomplish.

  Each quest is made up of one or more objectives, and a set of 
  rewards when all objectives are complete.

  Some quests are open for all levels, but some quests have a minimum
  and maximum level. Additionally, some quests require that you must
  have completed a previous quest.

  All and all, mini quests should be a lot of fun to complete!

  
  For more information, see: "help quest_commands"

